From: Oleksandr Natalenko <oleksandr@natalenko.name>
Subject: [pf-curated-6.12] archlinux: Arch Linux distribution patches

Re-cut from natalenko's pf-kernel branch archlinux-6.12 (tip 2f67aa51f8a9)
as a single bulk diff, restricted to the files this overlay's curation
kept on the 6.12 LTS slot. Source: codeberg.org/pf-kernel/linux.

Arch-Linux-specific patches that natalenko cherry-picked. New branch
on 6.12.
---
diff --git a/include/linux/user_namespace.h b/include/linux/user_namespace.h
index 7183e5aca2..56573371a2 100644
--- a/include/linux/user_namespace.h
+++ b/include/linux/user_namespace.h
@@ -159,6 +159,8 @@ static inline void set_userns_rlimit_max(struct user_namespace *ns,
 
 #ifdef CONFIG_USER_NS
 
+extern int unprivileged_userns_clone;
+
 static inline struct user_namespace *get_user_ns(struct user_namespace *ns)
 {
 	if (ns)
@@ -192,6 +194,8 @@ extern bool current_in_userns(const struct user_namespace *target_ns);
 struct ns_common *ns_get_owner(struct ns_common *ns);
 #else
 
+#define unprivileged_userns_clone 0
+
 static inline struct user_namespace *get_user_ns(struct user_namespace *ns)
 {
 	return &init_user_ns;
diff --git a/kernel/user_namespace.c b/kernel/user_namespace.c
index aa0b2e47f2..d74d857b16 100644
--- a/kernel/user_namespace.c
+++ b/kernel/user_namespace.c
@@ -22,6 +22,13 @@
